,=E2=80=9D the regulators  hastened to add. But I wonder=C2=A0if future ban=
king supervision will be more sensitive to things like industry diversifica=
tion among depositors, or the volatility of depositors=E2=80=99 industries.=
 If all of your depositors are in the same line of business, and if they ar=
e sometimes flush with cash and sometimes broke, then your bank is riskier.

The second conclusion=C2=A0is =E2=80=A6=C2=A0well, one way to put it is tha=
t=C2=A0the post-SVB actions have made bank deposits=C2=A0a lot safer, which=
