bank that has a lot of losses on held-to-maturity securities. And so in exc=
hange for that windfall the regulators should=C2=A0regulate those banks muc=
h more strictly, which will make them=C2=A0actually=C2=A0safer (and reduce =
the government=E2=80=99s exposure to their risks), but will also reduce the=
