=09As a matter of moral hazard, rescuing SVB=E2=80=99s depositors is fine;=
=09As a matter of moral hazard, zeroing SVB=E2=80=99s shareholders is good;=
 but=09As a matter of moral hazard, the right thing to do now is to=C2=A0pu=
nish other risky banks=E2=80=99 shareholders.

This is tricky! You are sort of =E2=80=A6=C2=A0prospectively punishing thos=
e shareholders? Punishing them in lieu of=C2=A0letting their banks fail?
