dium-sized bank that made some dumb rates bets, there is no reason to move =
your money now; the Fed has made it clear that it will support that bank. T=
his (probably!)=C2=A0takes run risk off the table for those banks, making t=
hem less likely to fail, making their stocks and bonds more valuable than t=
hey would be if the Fed hadn=E2=80=99t acted to limit contagion. (In actual=
