<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Signature Bank was seized by the government Su=
nday after regulators lost faith in management, according to New York offic=
ials.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CThe bank failed to provide reliable a=
nd consistent data, creating a significant crisis of confidence in the bank=
