</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">They can just do that! What <a href=3D"https:/=
/link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30835463.258425/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxv=
b21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDMtMTMvc3ZiLWNvdWxkbi10LWlnbm9=
yZS1pdHMtbG9zc2VzLWJ1dC10aGUtZmVkLWNhbj9jbXBpZD1CQkQwMzE0MjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRi=
Z1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMzAzMTQmd=
XRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cC083768b3" itemprop=
