00000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-b=
ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
  I said yesterday was</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Every=C2=A0<em>other=C2=A0</em>bank=E2=80=99s=
=C2=A0shareholders and bondholders and executives will benefit from those m=
easures [that the Fed and FDIC took to rescue SVB=E2=80=99s depositors]. If=
 you are an uninsured depositor at a medium-sized bank that made some dumb =
rates bets, there is no reason to move your money now; the Fed has made it =
clear that it will support that bank. This (probably!)=C2=A0<a href=3D"http=
s://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30835463.258425/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuY=
mxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDMtMTMvc3ZiLWFmdGVybWF0aC10=
aGVyZS1zLWxpdHRsZS1ldmlkZW5jZS1vZi1hLWZ1bGwtc2NhbGUtYmFua2luZy1jcmlzaXM_Y21=
waWQ9QkJEMDMxNDIzX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3=
NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjMwMzE0JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b=
8524a319a23cB2894c632" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-deco=
ration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00=
0000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">takes run risk o=
ff the table for those banks</a>, making them less likely to fail, making t=
heir stocks and bonds more valuable than they would be if the Fed hadn=E2=
=80=99t acted to limit contagion. (In actual fact many bank stocks=C2=A0are=
=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30835463.258=
