<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Credit Suisse Group AG said it found =E2=80=9C=
material weaknesses=E2=80=9D in its reporting and control procedures for th=
e past two years, after questions from US regulators last week.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The Zurich-based bank said Tuesday it will tak=
e steps to fix ineffective checks on the process it follows to pull togethe=
r its financial reports. But the firm said its statements for 2022 and 2021=
 =E2=80=9Cfairly present=E2=80=9D its financial condition.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There is never a great time for a bank to anno=
unce =E2=80=9Chey turns out we don=E2=80=99t really know what=E2=80=99s goi=
ng on at our bank,=E2=80=9D but this week does feel like a particularly bad=
 time.</p>
